      <heading>Tue Apr  3 (Shondai)    :: *Master at Arms*</heading>
      <slot>5</slot>
      <level>49</level>
      <author>0</author>
      <date>0</date>
      <text>*OOC Note:*
Hello all, I'm the new Master at Arms for the White Tower, there
alot of wonderful things in the works, including a new 
syllabus which is being carefully put into place, and 
a very hard effort to bring the glory back to the White Tower
that it once had. 

As we progress and grow together, I surely hope that we can 
get some activity in the guild and get a good base together. Alot
of people are bitter over others here, and that's never a 
good thing. Someday, the Rebels and the White Tower will clash, 
and the Tower will once again be reunited. In order to prepare 
for this, we must as a guild, come together, and get 
the Tower ready for the future.  Let us shake the ties that bind, 
and cast forth a fist high into the air torwards defeat, shaking it
as we charge forth to rebuild anew.

** IC **
-=Written in a superb handwriting, a note is posted here.=-

Let all who walk these halls be informed that Shondai Sudaki, 
formerly of Shienar, now hold the title of Master at Arms, 
respectfully promoted by the Amyrlin Seat with careful
consultation and consideration by my peers. Those who have
reason to seek an audience with me feel freely to enter 
my office, it is open to anyone who could need me.

Signed,
Shondai Sudaki, Master at Arms.
</text>
