      <slot>10</slot>
      <level>100</level>
      <author>0</author>
      <date>0</date>
      <text>For the crime of physical assault on an Aes Sedai, the Warder Rathan 
Dramiel is to be flogged, publicly, before the entire population of the 
White Tower.  Novices will be excused from lessons and chores and 
with Accepted, Trainees, Gaidin, and all Aes Sedai currently within 
the Tower, attend the Traitors Court to witness the each of the thirty 
lashes.  
 
Additionally, Rathan will be exiled from Tar Valon for at least one full 
year, and should he attempt to return to the island before this period 
expires, exiled until his death.
 
This punishment is deemed by the Hall of the Tower to be adequate 
retribution the crime.  Further action taken against the Warder by any 
individuals will be met with harsh judgement.

*sealed with the Flame of Tar Valon*
Elaida do Avriny a'Roihan
Keeper of the Flame
Watcher of the Seals
The Amyrlin Seat
</text>
