      <text>There is grim news that I must share with you all, my fellow sisters.
I have received pigeons bearing messages from the family Ezara...
Our beloved Lio, former Sitter of the Hall, has fallen in her homeland
of Shienar. The family relates that she and her warder, Toban, helped
to stem the most recent of attacks on the border, and in doing so,
surrendered their very lives. The messages are short, and do not give
a tremendous amount of detail, but it is made clear that the pair died
serving the Light and with honor. And for a Green, this is the highest
compliment. If there are any that wish to view the messages, I have
them in my quarters... This is a day of mourning for us all. Light
guard us, and protect the memory of Lio Ezara, Green Ajah.
 
Traya Amhranai
Green Ajah
</text>
